OL,3,C'We continue to fight': Family
OL,4,Caffected by birth defect linked to
OL,5,Cepilepsy drug
OL,7,FAnn O'Connor has been speaking to a
OL,8,Fmum from Cumbria who took Sodium
OL,9,FValproate during both her pregnancies.
OL,11,FA mum whose children were born with a
OL,12,Fbirth defect linked to epilepsy
OL,13,Fmedication has said she was not told
OL,14,Fabout the risks of taking the drug
OL,15,Fwhile she was pregnant.
OL,17,FNicola Stephens, from Burton-in-Kendal
OL,18,Fin Cumbria, took Sodium Valproate - a
OL,19,Fdrug used to treat her condition -
OL,20,Fwhile pregnant.
