OL,5,Cepilepsy drug
OL,7,FHer children, Oliver and Grace, have
OL,8,Fbeen diagnosed with Foetal Valproate
OL,9,FSyndrome, which is associated with
OL,10,Fautism, speech and development
OL,11,Fproblems.
OL,13,FOliver received the diagnosis when he
OL,14,Fwas five.
OL,16,F"When he got the diagnosis, it didn't
OL,17,Ffeel that scary. Now he's 20, it feels
OL,18,Fvery scary," she said.
