OL,7,F"It shouldn't be this hard. Everything
OL,8,Fwe have done for our children up until
OL,9,Fnow has been a fight and we continue
OL,10,Fto fight.
OL,12,F"How many of, them that are stalling
OL,13,Fthese decision, lie awake at night
OL,14,Fwondering what's going to happen to
OL,15,Ftheir children when we're not here?
