OL,3,C'We continue to fight': Family
OL,4,Caffected by birth defect linked to
OL,5,Cepilepsy drug
OL,7,F"Every night you fall into bed and
OL,8,Fit's going round in your head like,
OL,9,Fone day there's not going to be anyone
OL,10,Faround to ring their therapist, chase
OL,11,Ftheir appointment, to fight for their
OL,12,FPIP, to have their voices heard.
OL,14,F"One day they're not going to have
OL,15,Fthat, so we've got to do it now."
OL,17,FNicola Stephens said she wasn't aware
OL,18,Fof the risks of taking Sodium
OL,19,FValproate while pregnant.
