OL,5,Cepilepsy drug
OL,7,FFoetal Valproate Syndrome causes a
OL,8,Frange of neuro and physical
OL,9,Fdevelopmental conditions.
OL,11,FNicola's daughter Grace, 18, is hoping
OL,12,Fto study dance at university, while
OL,13,FOliver, who is 20, recently passed his
OL,14,Fdriving test after two years.
OL,16,FOliver said: "It's been a big hurdle
OL,17,Fto come over but having passed it, it
OL,18,Ffeels like a big relief really in my
OL,19,Flife."
