OL,7,FA statement from the Department of
OL,8,FHealth and Social Care in February
OL,9,F2026 said: "This is a complex issue
OL,10,Fand our priority is to ensure any
OL,11,Fresponse is fair, balanced and
OL,12,Fsensitive to those affected.
OL,14,F"We are carefully considering the
OL,15,Frecommendations within the Hughes
OL,16,FReport... and we aim to provide an
OL,17,Fupdate in due course."
OL,19,FA similar statement was also given in
OL,20,FFebruary 2025.
